ss=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89212879aaf72d02d5b90772bcfd05eb4fca9466","tid":2358133,"uid":260335,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T02:41:07.000Z","msg":"同個細路女影幾張相 又話人戀童 <br />\n咁多張相挑幾張出黎 同藍絲一撚樣無老<br />\n<br />\n見到得意細路女 得cctoy會話人戀童<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd9a47794f5c2369c5fab5131923e2fbf9c497b1","tid":2358133,"uid":204180,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T02:43:49.000Z","msg":"做人做事都好未到最後一刻唔可以比人帶到風向<br />\n<br />\n絕望感真係會由好有信念變成懷疑自己<br />\n<br />\n有時自己決定要去做 果一刻就要盡力做<br />\n<br />\n有咩後果 只有上天先知<br />\n<br />\n我發覺有d巴打未必係5毛搞事，但因為大勢所趨，令自己信念有動搖。<br />\n<br />\n繼而開始用事實係殘酷，勝者為王呢d好功利主義既詞語去掩飾自己對信心既動搖。<br />\n<br />\n有d事係岩就岩 你就算用強權掩蓋事實<br />\n<br />\n果件事都係真理黎 我真係好討厭現代人比功利主義磨滅左做人既基本原則。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbb108e2ae02da6b8d78d9e303c10cab33e7de6c","tid":2358133,"uid":10637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd23135ee0021c118b7a805a24abae23b84c1320","tid":2358133,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"396f78385bf42d41a2524a46269d5ccead8b38c5","tid":2358133,"uid":13724,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"21720b08a865e054992081015542527fea55c116","tid":2358133,"uid":260335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T02:16:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T02:39:03.000Z","msg":"反而有啲期待拜登上台後， 美國強硬態度不變嘅話應該會仲好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T02:39:51.000Z","msg":"可能重演16年侵上任嗰陣既高登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T02:47:30.000Z","msg":"商家係可以收買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca0afa3e84b90664bc80061a1c65fa79e2efe4d8","tid":2358133,"uid":260335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T02:57:55.000Z","msg":"本身開頭同大部分人一樣<br />\n頭幾日都keep fight<br />\n之後一路見到機會愈來愈細<br />\n<br />\n但1月6呢單野係真係令我多番左小小信心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我普通人 冇搵好多料 亦唔識d咩理論啦<br />\n純講常識同邏輯 1月6呢場大龍鳳 <br />\n<br />\ntrump唔係有信心係手既 唔會搞咁多野<br />\n佢一句同彭斯握下手降溫已經可以落晒台<br />\n再加仲有好多跡象啦 本身1月6呢個日子 真係2個月前聽到依家<br />\ntrump果邊一直講淨係care 1月6同1月20<br />\nharris又未辭職 同埋佢地果邊唔敢講太多野<br />\n<br />\n但我仍然覺得軍管呢招機會極微 <br />\n軍管會有 但一定唔會係關鍵<br />\n當然trump有軍方支持係關鍵 <br />\n最後反cup藍圖 都係靠 講左好耐既證據<br />\n之後上supreme court/軍事法庭 <br />\n期間可能會有軍管 係1月20或者早小小前後 <br />\n(當然機會都係奇蹟 但1月6之後係加左小小信心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n笑到我肚痛"},{"pid":"06f41f084143ad433182a9e0afbfbaf29181be3d","tid":2358133,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fbb108e2ae02da6b8d78d9e303c10cab33e7de6c","tid":2358133,"uid":10637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd23135ee0021c118b7a805a24abae23b84c1320","tid":2358133,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"396f78385bf42d41a2524a46269d5ccead8b38c5","tid":2358133,"uid":13724,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T02:39:03.000Z","msg":"反而有啲期待拜登上台後， 美國強硬態度不變嘅話應該會仲好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T02:39:51.000Z","msg":"可能重演16年侵上任嗰陣既高登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T02:47:30.000Z","msg":"商家係可以收買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T03:01:35.000Z","msg":"2邊都係商家，就算侵自己都係.... 講真， 講到同支那有貿易關係=奶共呢樣概念我覺得太極端... <br />\n<br />\n我覺得啲國家反而要做一樣嘢， 就係應該要識收放。支那要買咪賣俾佢， 但同時要教識啲支那人佢俾錢只係買件貨/服務， 其他嘢例如批評你無人權乜乜77係唔包嘅"},{"pid":"c253374270d51ea30ee205301e7f72d272838e95","tid":2358133,"uid":260335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T03:06:22.000Z","msg":"佢根本就無退路，唯有同已經成為命運共同體嘅愛國者拼死一戰先有機會<br />\n<br />\n就算佢最後真係輸，真係要身敗名裂，我好肯定佢唔會放棄，會戰鬥到最後一刻，因為佢本來就係咁樣嘅人先會有咁多忠誠嘅人民支持<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1af6174f1a946e9fa27fce92e948bd6483f5d78a","tid":2358133,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c253374270d51ea30ee205301e7f72d272838e95","tid":2358133,"uid":260335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T03:06:22.000Z","msg":"佢根本就無退路，唯有同已經成為命運共同體嘅愛國者拼死一戰先有機會<br />\n<br />\n就算佢最後真係輸，真係要身敗名裂，我好肯定佢唔會放棄，會戰鬥到最後一刻，因為佢本來就係咁樣嘅人先會有咁多忠誠嘅人民支持<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T03:09:56.000Z","msg":"好似睇戲咁"}]}